<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title>


<para>The <tag>phrase</tag> element in DocBook has no specific semantic.
It is provided as a wrapper around a selection of words smaller than a
paragraph so that it is possible to provide an
<tag class="attribute">xml:id</tag> or other attributes for them.
</para>

<para>For example, if you are making note of changes to a document using one
of the effectivity attributes, you might use <tag>phrase</tag> to 
mark up specific sentences with revisions.
</para>

